Another option would be a custom callback if you dont want to pass in too many options, like

``` php
<?php
XmlSecurity::scan($xml, $dom, function ($xml, $dom) {
    return $dom->loadHTML($xml, LIBXML_HTML_NOIMPLIED | LIBXML_HTML_NODEFDTD);
});
```

